UNITED STATES v. HARVEY & OUTERBRIDGE. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. January 30, 1906.) No. 115 (3,522). Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. For decision below, see 137 Fed. 816, reversing a decision of the Board of United States General Appraisers.

Before TOWNSEND and COXE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Reversed in open court on consent
